Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.14,0:54:04.24,ThemeCN,,0,0,0,,{\fscx140\fsp-10\fad(250,250)}来畅想两个人的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.49,0:54:09.77,ThemeCN,,0,0,0,,{\fscx140\fsp-10\fad(250,250)}布满结痂伤口 无法治愈的心
